COMPONENTS COVERED
------------------

1. GAME ENGINES
   - classify-and-place engine and all content packs
   - kitchen engine
   - inkblot engine (Rorschach-inspired cognitive assessment)
   - All future engines developed under this repository

2. BIOMETRIC FRAMEWORK
   - biomet.js — universal biometric measurement engine
   - telemetry.js — unified telemetry sender
   - auto-save.js — session capture system
   - show-metrics.js — clinical metrics display
   - mood-modals.js — projective color assessment
   - input-calibration.js — input baseline measurement
   - All cognitive metric calculations and clinical flag algorithms

3. CONTENT PACKS
   - La Ferretería de Berugo (90 items, 9 categories, 7 missions)
   - El Almacén de Don Tito (79 items, 9 categories, 7 missions)
   - Electrodomésticos El Rayo (61 items, 8 categories, 7 missions)
   - La Librería de la Seño Marta (72 items, 8 categories, 7 missions)
   - Desafío Milanesas — Supermarket (44 items, 6 categories)
   - All future content packs

4. THERAPEUTIC GAMES
   - Cortadora de Césped (lawn-mower) — spatial planning
   - Organizador de Medicación (pill-organizer) — pharmacological praxis
   - Desafío Milanesas (super-market) — reading + episodic recall
   - Cocinero Neuronal (neuro-chef) — signal detection theory
   - Memoria de Medicación (medication-memory) — working memory
   - Mi Rutina Diaria (daily-routine) — ADL sequencing
   - Heladera Inteligente (fridge-logic) — food safety classification
   - All future games developed under this platform

5. CLINICAL ASSESSMENT METHODOLOGY
   - 140+ biometric variables captured per game session
   - 14 clinical constructs across 7 neuropsychological domains
   - Luria/Lezak/Miyake theoretical framework implementation
   - Reliable Change Index (RCI) based change detection
   - Cluster classification system (FUNCIONAL/HIPOACTIVO/HIPERACTIVO/DESORGANIZADO)
   - Longitudinal baseline detection algorithms
   - Normative population database schema and methodology

6. DATABASE SCHEMAS AND RPCS
   - All Supabase migrations (zykos_* tables)
   - Authentication RPC functions (zykos_register, zykos_login, zykos_validate_session)
   - Session management and telemetry schemas
   - Hash-based data integrity verification system

7. PLATFORM ARCHITECTURE
   - Multi-tenant B2B deployment model
   - Pack-based content system with JSON schema
   - Engine-agnostic game framework
   - Regional compliance packages (EU GDPR, USA HIPAA, Argentina ReNaPDiS)

